+# LSP Integration Design
+
+## Overview
+
+Language Server Protocol (LSP) integration for OpenClaw providing IDE-like features: diagnostics, hover, go-to-definition, references, and completion.
+
+## Milestone 1: LspManager
+
+### LspManager Class
+
+Manages the lifecycle of LSP servers.
+
+```typescript
+interface LspServerConfig {
+  name: string;
+  command: string;
+  args?: string[];
+  env?: Record<string, string>;
+  rootUri?: string;
+  initializationOptions?: Record<string, unknown>;
+}
+
+interface LspSession {
+  serverId: string;
+  state: ServerState;
+  process: ChildProcess | null;
+  capabilities: ServerCapabilities | null;
+}
+
+class LspManager {
+  constructor(private readonly workspaceRoot: string);
+  registerServer(id: string, config: LspServerConfig): void;
+  unregisterServer(id: string): void;
+  startServer(id: string): Promise<void>;
+  stopServer(id: string): Promise<void>;
+  getCapabilities(id: string): ServerCapabilities | null;
+  sendRequest<T>(id: string, method: string, params: unknown): Promise<T>;
+  sendNotification(id: string, method: string, params: unknown): void;
+  onEvent(id: string, handler: (event: LspEvent) => void): void;
+}
+```
+
+## Milestone 2: LSP Tool Definitions
+
+### Tool Names
+
+- `lsp_diagnostics` - Get current diagnostics for a file
+- `lsp_hover` - Get hover information at a position
+- `lsp_definition` - Go to definition
+- `lsp_references` - Find all references
+- `lsp_completion` - Get completion items
+
+### Tool Schemas
+
+```typescript
+// lsp_diagnostics
+{ fileUri: string }
+
+// lsp_hover
+{ fileUri: string, line: number, character: number }
+
+// lsp_definition
+{ fileUri: string, line: number, character: number }
+
+// lsp_references
+{ fileUri: string, line: number, character: number, includeDeclaration?: boolean }
+
+// lsp_completion
+{ fileUri: string, line: number, character: number, triggerKind?: number }
+```
+
+## Milestone 3: Extension → Language → LSP Server Mapping
+
+### Language Mapping Table
